2001-06-10  Peter Novodvorsky  <nidd@altlinux.ru>

	* lists.c (listTypeList): Classes added; fixes PR gnats/62.
	(getGnatsFile): Handle ListClasses.
	* query.h (e_lists): ListClasses added.

